From 294bb8d8f5c2db1a5a61bb930412783b0240ba9a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 02:09:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add React Router navigation and password reset flow
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Replace useState page-switching with react-router-dom v7 (BrowserRouter +
  Routes/Route); pages now have real URLs (/login, /register, /dashboard,
  /admin, /forgot-password, /reset-password) so refresh and back/forward work
- Remove setPage prop drilling from Navbar, Login, Register, UserDashboard;
  each component uses useNavigate() directly
- Add protected routes: /dashboard redirects to /login if unauthenticated;
  /admin redirects to / if not role_id=1
- Add forgot-password and reset-password pages with matching UI style
- Add AuthController::forgotPassword() and ::resetPassword() backend methods;
  tokens are SHA-256-hashed before storage, expire in 1 hour, single-use
- Add /api/auth/forgot-password and /api/auth/reset-password routes in index.php
- Add password_resets.sql migration for the new table
- Add api.auth.forgotPassword() and api.auth.resetPassword() in api.js
- Add "Mot de passe oublié ?" link in Login form

https://claude.ai/code/session_01Sd2VC7cYZDyiqtfaideRtz
